              "<p>This 75-minute class will&nbsp;explore&nbsp;<em>bhandas</em>&nbsp;(energy locks) in standing asanas and in poses like&nbsp;<em>marichyasana</em>,&nbsp;cow face pose, camel, dolphin, and more.</p>",
